<h1>CARDORA Account Deletion</h1>

<p>
Users can permanently delete their CARDORA account and associated data at any time.
</p>

<h2>How to delete your account</h2>

<ol>
<li>Open the CARDORA app.</li>
<li>Go to <strong>Profile</strong>.</li>
<li>Open <strong>Settings</strong>.</li>
<li>Select <strong>Delete Account</strong>.</li>
<li>Confirm the deletion.</li>
</ol>

<h2>Deleted data</h2>

<ul>
<li>User account</li>
<li>Collection</li>
<li>Wishlist</li>
<li>Portfolio</li>
<li>Profile information</li>
<li>App settings</li>
</ul>

<h2>Retained data</h2>

<p>
Some information may be retained temporarily only when required by law or for fraud prevention.
</p>

